        button(style='display: none;', onclick='clickedButton2()') Add article 2
        button(style='display: none;', onclick='clickedButton1()') Add article 1
        button(style='display: none;', onclick='sortArticles()') Sort
        .container
            .top(style='text-align: !left; margin-bottom: -30px; margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.5;', onmouseover='this.style.opacity=\'1\'; document.getElementById(\'menuItems\').style.opacity=\'1\'; document.getElementById(\'quotes\').style.display=\'none\';  document.getElementById(\'menuItems\').style.display=\'block\' ', onmouseout='this.style.opacity=\'0.5\';document.getElementById(\'menuItems\').style.opacity=\'0\'; document.getElementById(\'menuItems\').style.display=\'none\'; document.getElementById(\'quotes\').style.display=\'block\'; ')                
                
                div(style='height: 280;')
                    h1
                        a(href='/')
                            img(style='margin-bottom: 30px; margin-right: 20px;', src='../img/wikivisLogo.png', title='Daily Data Insights - Applied Data Science', height='150', width='150')
                        #menuItems(style='margin-bottom: 74px; margin-top: -40px; display: none; opacity: 0; padding-top: 20px;')
                            a#tagline(style='opacity: 0.4; color: rgb(54,154,104);') about
                            |  :: 
                            a(style='color: rgb(9,106,156);', href='/') showroom
                            |  :: 
                            a#tagline2(style='color: rgb(153,0,0);', href='/create/') create
                        blockquote#quotes(style='margin-top: -40px; padding-top: 20px; display: block;')
                            |
            
            #content
                .container
                    .post
                        p
                            strong Daily Data Insights
                            |  is a platform to present, rate and share.

                        p
                            | DDI is developed by 
                            a(href='http://github.com/daumann') Dietmar Aumann
                            |  as an independent and nonprofit project. I love clean and minimalistic design and enjoy losing myself in interesting data sets around the world. You can find some of those projects in the 
                            a(href='http://www.dailydatainsights.com') showroom
                            | . While not always daily, new content is added regularly. 
                        
                        p
                            | Tools used include 
                            a(href='http://www.gnu.org/software/bash/') Bash
                            |  (mostly data extraction and transformation),  
                            a(href='http://www.r-project.org/') R
                            | , 
                            a(href='https://www.python.org/') Python
                            | , 
                            a(href='http://spark.apache.org/') Spark
                            | , 
                            a(href='https://mahout.apache.org/') Mahout
                            |  (analytics, machine learning) and the awesome 
                            a(href='http://d3js.org/') d3.js
                            |  library (data visualisation). This website is built on  
                            a(href='http://nodejs.org/') Node.js
                            |  with the help of 
                            a(href='http://expressjs.com/') Express
                            |  and 
                            a(href='http://www.mongodb.org/') MongoDB
                            | .
                        
                        p 
                            | Don't miss an update, like DDI on: 
                            a( href='http://www.facebook.com/dailydatainsights') Facebook!
                        
                        div(style="border-top: 1px solid #e7e7e7; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px;")

                        p   I would love to hear from you.  Have suggestions for improving this website, questions, or inquiries?

                        div.addCommentForms(style="clear: both;")
                            form
                                div
                                    div
                                        input#emailSender.form-control(style="background: #f9f9f9; margin-top: 10px;",type="email", class="nameTxt", name="email",placeholder='Your email')
                                    div
                                        textarea#emailContent.form-control(style="background: #f9f9f9; margin-top: 11px;",placeholder='Your message...', rows='3', name='comment')
                                    div
                                        input.btn.btn-default.btn-outline(onclick="sendEmail()" style="margin-top: 10px;", type="submit", value="Send Email")
                        

